dct_title_s: UMass Amherst Libraries Data and Datasets
dct_description_sm: Spatial datasets deposited in ScholarWorks@UMassAmherst, the institutional repository at the University of Massachusetts Amherst.
dct_rights_sm: The Data & Datasets Repository is an open access repository in ScholarWorks@UMassAmherst. Holdings are freely available.
